<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <meta name="description" content="Personal website for Cristiano Silva Jr.">
        <title>Hello!</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.css">
        <link rel="icon" href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ishiikurisu/crisjr-eng-br/master/assets/logo.png">
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Rubik" rel="stylesheet">
        <style>
            {{.Style}}
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>

        <div class="header">
            <div class="home-menu pure-menu pure-menu-horizontal pure-menu-fixed">
                <a class="pure-menu-heading" href="/"><i class="fa fa-smile-o"></i>
					Cris Silva Jr.
				</a>

                <ul class="pure-menu-list">
                    <li class="pure-menu-item"><a href="office" class="pure-menu-link pure-menu-selected">Office</a></li>
                    <li class="pure-menu-item"><a href="garage" class="pure-menu-link">Garage</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h2 class="content-head is-center">Offered Services</h2>

            <div class="pure-g">
                <div class="l-box-lrg is-center pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-2-5">
                    <img width="200" alt="File Icons" class="pure-img-responsive" src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ishiikurisu/crisjr-eng-br/master/assets/unb.png">
                </div>
                <div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-3-5">
                    <h2 class="content-head">Control &amp; Automation Engineer</h2>
                    <p>
                        My specialty is digital signal processing, built upon my experiences in the biomedical engineering field. My strongest skills come from computer engineering, ranging from electronic circuit design to modern software development methodologies; and help me be part of teams to build and maintain complex systems. I also have experiences with web development and computer systems' administration, so I can deliver and develop better and more integrated solutions.

                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="l-box-lrg is-center pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-2-5">
                    <img width="200" alt="File Icons" class="pure-img-responsive" src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ishiikurisu/crisjr-eng-br/master/assets/labneuro.png">
                </div>
                <div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-3-5">
                    <h2 class="content-head">Personal Organizer</h2>
                    <p>
                        To make better use of my engineering skills, I have developed solid organization skills, that can be used not only for companies and teams, but also for individuals that seek to control their time, their workspaces and their projects. I provide training and consulting to help others dominate their workflow, complete their tasks and live a better life.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="content manager-joe">
            <h2 class="content-head is-center">Previous Experiences</h2>

            <div class="pure-g">
                <div class="l-box-lrg is-center pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-2-5">
                    <img width="200" alt="File Icons" class="pure-img-responsive" src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ishiikurisu/crisjr-eng-br/master/assets/unb.png">
                </div>
                <div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-3-5">
                    <h2 class="content-head"><a class="black-header-link" href="http://unb.br/">Mechatronics Engineering</a></h2>
                    <p>
                        I study Mechatronics Engineering in the University of Brasilia.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="l-box-lrg is-center pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-2-5">
                    <img width="200" alt="File Icons" class="pure-img-responsive" src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ishiikurisu/crisjr-eng-br/master/assets/labneuro.png">
                </div>
                <div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-3-5">
                    <h2 class="content-head"><a class="black-header-link" href="http://www.biologiaanimal.unb.br/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=8&Itemid=14">Researcher at the  Laboratory of Neuroscience and Behaviour</a></h2>
                    <p>
                        I developed dedicated software for biomedical signal processing and psychological data processing, such as <a href="https://github.com/lab-neuro-comp/P2" class="black-header-link">Protolize!</a>, <a href="https://github.com/ishiikurisu/Scalemate" class="black-header-link">Scalemate</a>, and an implementation of the Stop Signal Task. Each one of them is presented in their own scientific publications.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="l-box-lrg is-center pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-2-5">
                    <img width="200" alt="File Icons" class="pure-img-responsive ieee-img" src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ishiikurisu/crisjr-eng-br/master/assets/ieee.png">
                </div>
                <div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-3-5">
                    <h2 class="content-head"><a class="black-header-link" href="http://www.ieee.org/index.html">IEEE Member</a></h2>
                    <p>
                        As organizational president of <a class="black-header-link" href="https://www.facebook.com/sensesunb/">EMBS UnB</a>, I help keep our whole chapter on tracks, directing our efforts to complete events such as talks on biomedical engineering and time management; and the <a href="https://www.possibilita.bmd.br" class="black-header-link">Possibilita</a> project, an initiative focused on educating the general public on how to create their own assistive devices.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        As the general secretary of the <a href="https://www.facebook.com/IEEEComputerSocietyUnB" class="black-header-link">Computer Society UnB</a>, I organize the <a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/1009735115784291/" class="black-header-link">Coding Dojo UnB</a> and maintain the chapter's teams to complete and expand their projects.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="l-box-lrg is-center pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-2-5">
                    <img width="200" alt="File Icons" class="pure-img-responsive" src="https://github.com/ishiikurisu/unicows/raw/master/app/assets/images/logo-transparent.png">
                </div>
                <div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-3-5">
                    <h2 class="content-head"><a class="black-header-link" href="https://unicows.herokuapp.com">Founder of Unicows</a></h2>
                    <p>
                        I helped found the Unicows store, setting our internal structure and building the website.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="content ">
            {{.Footer}}
        </div>

        <script type="text/javascript">
            {{.Script}}
        </script>
    </body>
</html>
